    <fr:p>Condition (b) of <fr:ref
addr="hodge-theory-ii-4.4.8"
href="hodge-theory-ii-4.4.8.xml"
number="4.4.8" /> cannot be satisfied at every place of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[Z]]></fr:tex>, since the Hodge structure would then be locally constant, which (by <fr:ref
addr="hodge-theory-ii-4.1.3.3"
href="hodge-theory-ii-4.1.3.3.xml"
