addr="hodge-theory-ii-4.4.8"
href="hodge-theory-ii-4.4.8.xml"
number="4.4.8" />).
      Taking <fr:ref
addr="hodge-theory-ii-4.4.3"
href="hodge-theory-ii-4.4.3.xml"
taxon="Reminder"
number="4.4.3" /> into account, this finishes the proof.</fr:p>
